<p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 为促使同学们主动探索心理知识，提升心理素养，学会妥善处理人际关系，搭建情感共鸣的桥梁，经济管理学院于11月27日晚6：30在A10-408开展心理情景剧大赛。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">比赛现场</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;在比赛过程中，各参赛队伍通过一个个触动心灵的故事，用独特的戏剧形式，展现同学们在日常学习与生活里所经历的情感波动。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024881339076128.png" title="1733024881339076128.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111820.png" width="537" height="331" style="width: 537px; height: 331px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024888177007893.png" title="1733024888177007893.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111825.png" width="542" height="299" style="width: 542px; height: 299px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024896273042439.png" title="1733024896273042439.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111831.png" width="550" height="334" style="width: 550px; height: 334px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 舞台之上，灯光与暗影交织，角色们用鲜活的演绎将抽象的心理波澜化作可见的情节起伏。如静水深流，将细腻的情感潜藏于台词的缝隙、动作的微澜；似惊涛拍岸，把内心的冲突与挣扎借激烈的场景碰撞、情感的澎湃宣泄。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024905447019595.png" title="1733024905447019595.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111836.png" width="549" height="341" style="width: 549px; height: 341px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024914872020192.png" title="1733024914872020192.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111841.png" width="555" height="337" style="width: 555px; height: 337px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024922901030534.png" title="1733024922901030534.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111846.png" width="561" height="302" style="width: 561px; height: 302px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 每一组表演结束后，评委老师从剧本深度、表演技巧、情感表达等多个维度进行了全面而细致的点评。他们不仅肯定了同学们的努力和才华，也提出了宝贵的建议。</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024934887044674.png" title="1733024934887044674.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111851.png" width="574" height="453" style="width: 574px; height: 453px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">比赛结果</span></strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 经过评委老师对参赛作品的细致评审，本次比赛的结果已经出炉。以下是获奖名单：</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024945155040739.png" title="1733024945155040739.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111856.png" width="604" height="241" style="width: 604px; height: 241px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">结语</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本次比赛不仅成功搭建了一个展示才华的平台，更是在传播心理安全知识、传递心灵力量方面发挥了积极作用。在未来的旅途中，愿同学们以更加坚定的步伐和宽广的胸怀，勇敢地迎接生活中的每一缕阳光和每一次风雨，拥抱生活的无限可能！</span></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241201/1733024957305066347.png" title="1733024957305066347.png" alt="微信图片_20241201111903.png" width="599" height="354" style="width: 599px; height: 354px;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span><br/></p><p><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>